{"tid":2381918,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"28歲男涉去年元旦管有武器原判社會服務令 律政司覆核得直 改判監禁2個月","createTime":"2021-01-27T02:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T06:45:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2b85c3be47d730e7a37dcb4ac0c48c45d84cf2b3","tid":2381918,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:39:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13249&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv9UqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=418e8f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13249</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第八庭 <br />\n#何俊堯裁判官 #覆核聆訊<br />\n👤陳(27)  #20200101中環<br />\n<br />\n控罪(2)管有違禁武器：<br />\n被控於年1月1日在香港站公共運輸交匯處出入口外， 管有一把裝有彈簧的摺刀。<br />\n<br />\n控罪(3)管有物品意圖損壞財產：<br />\n被控於同日同地， 管有一個打火機及一罐噴油漆。<br />\n<br />\n何官在2020年8月18日判處被告100小時社會服務令，今律政司不服刑期過輕，向原審裁判官提出覆核。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n結果：<br />\n法庭接納律政司的覆核申請<br />\n<br />\n刑罰更改如下：<br />\n改為6個月監禁(量刑起點)<br />\n但考慮各因素後，最後刑期為監禁2個月，同期執行。"},{"pid":"dd3ee149c86a221b63d35229c65de918335c7865","tid":2381918,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82721fbb6cd5900bf978268c1c6a34a0fa2c1a18","tid":2381918,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:40:05.000Z","msg":"何官跪低咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e6ad3f30cca69141b96d9d2e318fcf71cdf9cf","tid":2381918,"uid":357803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"82721fbb6cd5900bf978268c1c6a34a0fa2c1a18","tid":2381918,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:40:05.000Z","msg":"何官跪低咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy